# AST-Grep Preference for Code Search

Prefer ast-grep over grep/rg for structural code searches:

```bash
ast-grep --lang tsx -p '<pattern>'
```

## Example patterns:

```bash
# Find async functions
ast-grep --lang typescript -p 'async function $NAME($$$) { $$$ }'

# Find React components
ast-grep --lang tsx -p 'export function $COMPONENT($$$) { $$$ }'

# Find method calls
ast-grep --lang typescript -p '$OBJ.methodName($$$)'
```

Fall back to grep for simple string literals or non-code searches.
